  "rationale": "Single sanctioned hero bookend reusing the project pattern hero-display-over-staggered-media (novelty adapt, seededFrom the project hero). Only the image-count axis is varied: the media cluster grows from two to three hard-edged photographs, all with declared registration and an explicit back\u2192front z-order (counter-media back, hero-media mid, overlap-media front). The portrait inset crosses the base image's bottom edge on the right while the new counter-media crosses the left edge as a back layer, balancing the cluster left/right. Centered didone display title carries the sole gold accent on the dark inverse surface; eyebrow, headline, support, and CTA copy are verbatim; spacing, type tiers, and palette match the seed."
